content.description: Each bubble represents the sum of measures for accounts owned by [Owner.Name] The total time to complete actions on their accounts was [sum_Interactions.SUMTimeToAction], over a total of [sum_Interactions.TotalClicks] clicks,  spread over [sum_Interactions.UniqueSessionKey] sessions involving [sum_Interactions.UniqueUserCount] users. The total time to complete these actions was [sum_Interactions.SumStallTime] and produced a data quality score of [avg_DataQualityScore]. All of this relates to leads with a predicted annual revenue of [sum_AnnualRevenue].
